'''Niragire Marie France''' ni Umunyarwandakazi ukora kandi agakina filime ndetse akaba n'umushoramari<ref>https://igihe.com/amakuru/u-rwanda/article/niragire-marie-france-wamenyekanye-nka-sonia-muri-film-yibarutse-umuhungu</ref>, niwe washinze ndetse uyoboye '''Genesis TV Rwanda,''' kandi akaba yarabashije gushobora gukina muri filime 8 zuruhererekane<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/187915</ref>

== '''amasomo''' ==
Yize muri kaminuza ahagana za 2008 aho yigaga ubukerarugendo n' icungamutungo, arinaho yaje kugira amahirwe yo gutangira gukina filime abifashijwemo n'inshuti ye biganaga<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/187915</ref>. kaminuza yayirangije muri 2012.  

== umwuga wa filime ==
Marie France nyuma yo kwiga yakomeje umwuga wo gukina filime abifatanya nakandi kazi kajyanye nibyo yize aho yakinnye filime nka Inzozi, Ubudasanzwe, Imbarutso, Anita nizindi<ref>https://ibyamamare.com/niragire-marie-france-wamamaye-muri-cinema-nyarwanda-yagejeje-mu-rwanda-imodoka-yagatangazaamafoto/</ref>
